Source: pg-rrf
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~), cargo, clang
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/yuiseki/pg_rrf

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-rrf
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pg-rrf
Depends: postgresql-PGVERSION, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Reciprocal rank fusion functions for PostgreSQL
 pg_rrf provides Reciprocal Rank Fusion scoring functions for hybrid search
 workloads inside PostgreSQL. This package builds the pgrx extension for
 PostgreSQL 14 through 17 with cargo-pgrx 0.17.0.
